metadata.name: Mystical Perception  #1/10
metadata.description:
This piece was created based on personal psychedelic experiences.  
The hands represent creation while the eyes represent presence and consciousness. 
These images are abundant in my visuals and have become a huge integrated part of my artwork style. The eyes crying cosmic tears, because the beauty of the ineffable truth is too much to bear for human eyes, and the emotions felt build up and the tears flow uncontrollably. 

I watched my hands move through dimensions, like a dance, creating impossible forms and sensations. Everything was harmonious, beautiful and vaguely uncomfortable 

Digital Painting  
Completed 2021  
3300 x 2550  
300 dpi
